items.title: Flag raised as part of Tribe's clinch celebration
items.summary: The Indians didn't get to officially clinch their second straight American League Central title after their win on Saturday, so instead, the celebration -- made possible by the Twins' loss later Saturday night -- began in front of a raucous crowd before Sunday's series finale against the Royals.
